<!-- index.html -->
<script>
    // Check if mobile
    if (window.innerWidth < 768) {
        window.location.href = 'mobile-invoice.html';
    } else {
        window.location.href = 'desktop-invoice.html';
    }
</script>
```

## File Structure:
```
Your GitHub Repository/
├── index.html (detector/router)
├── desktop-invoice.html (your current version)
└── mobile-invoice.html (new mobile version)
